Package: hsa-snoop
Version: PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Stephen Bates <sbates@raithlin.com>
Depends: systemd
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: HSA/HIP AQL queue snooper with Prometheus metrics exporter
 hsa-snoop monitors AMD GPU HSA/HIP AQL command queues at the kernel level
 using kprobes or bpftrace. When installed via this package it runs as a
 systemd service in Prometheus mode, exposing live GPU queue metrics at
 http://localhost:9488/metrics.
